02:13:10,620 --> 02:13:15,421
They soar high up in the sky.

1356
02:13:16,292 --> 02:13:18,283
l'm taking Arjun with me.

1357
02:13:18,561 --> 02:13:20,290
lf l leave him here he will become

1358
02:13:20,563 --> 02:13:22,360
another version of you.

1359
02:13:22,699 --> 02:13:26,567
One of you is enough for this world.

1360
02:13:27,303 --> 02:13:31,706
You will never
understand why this happened.

1361
02:13:32,442 --> 02:13:38,847
Because it's a word you've
never known or experienced...

1362
02:13:39,782 --> 02:13:40,840
Love.

1363
02:13:42,051 --> 02:13:46,317
Please don't try to find us. lf you
come within a 100 kilometers of us,

1364
02:13:46,523 --> 02:13:49,515
The police will know you beat Arjun.

1365
02:13:49,926 --> 02:13:53,327
Legally, it's a criminal offence.

1366
02:13:54,330 --> 02:13:57,322
Arjun can be a lot
more than just your slave.

1367
02:13:57,667 --> 02:14:00,329
He needs a family, not a cage.

1368
02:14:00,737 --> 02:14:04,798
He needs a future, which l will make
sure he gets, whatever the cost...

1369
02:14:05,475 --> 02:14:09,741
Congratulations on your new wife,
your new daughter, your new life.

1370
02:14:10,346 --> 02:14:12,405
Your son, Rohan.

1371
02:14:13,416 --> 02:14:22,552
ls life over?. Or is
it about to begin?

1372
02:14:23,693 --> 02:14:32,362
ls this nightfall?
Or is it a new dawn?

1373
02:14:32,769 --> 02:14:38,366
Will the future bring comfort?

1374
02:14:41,711 --> 02:14:48,776
Or will bring us to a crossroad?

1375
02:14:50,787 --> 02:14:58,717
Who knows what lies ahead...